                hero_ey: 'Common questions',
                hero_h: 'Answers to the questions<br>we hear <em>most.</em>',
                hero_p: 'From the best time to visit to what to pack and how to book — everything you need before your Amazon expedition.',
                cat_planning: 'Planning', cat_tours: 'The Tours', cat_expect: 'What to Expect', cat_health: 'Health & Safety', cat_booking: 'Booking',
